                    "value": "<p>Area <strong>C36</strong> and <strong>C37</strong>.</p>\n<hr />\n<p>A typical ghost can stray only a short distance from where it was killed or the place it haunts. A typical limit is 120 feet. Some ghosts are instead bound to a room, building, item, or creature that was special to it rather than a location.</p>"
